{"tid":2270782,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2021DSE自修] 有冇自修英文既人想補底上3","createTime":"2020-11-04T08:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T03:27:10.000Z","uid":125535,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7bdb436bb481cde4315cb68e1822a2383ca04f","tid":2270782,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 黎緊有個補底小組比自修英文既巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為斷腳而入唔到U/asso既case實在太多太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我地今次個班就係針對呢個情況嘅巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n形式係每次個半鐘, 老師會同大家操返一啲基本技巧,同大家認清目標同埋清楚攞3嘅條件,當然都會操返卷一二三<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個小組係定位俾lv2或以下既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以係Google Form留低聯絡方法, 會再pm詳情<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/xJmG7UQ9prKARE3x5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FxJmG7UQ9prKARE3x5&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3Vcyg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=97586055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/xJmG7UQ9prKARE3x5</a><br />\n<br />\n日期: 逢星期一 (9/11, 16/11, 23/11, 30/11, 7/12,14/12)<br />\n時期: 早上11點半 - 下午1點<br />\n地點: 荔枝角既社區中心<br />\n人數: 本身已經差唔多成團~ 如果最後太多人報會按各位巴絲需要&amp;情況再處理<br />\n收費: $100/6堂<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><span class=\"brown\">利申: 社福機構舉辦既, 已補貼, 冇賺到大家一分一毫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong>利申擔心既巴絲可以起下我底,一直都有幫開自修生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1be47698c79d3a84655160a353c1899a0003313c","tid":2270782,"uid":278118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"好人一世平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16af90201c5d48f6823fc2d